Installation
------------

Install dependencies in your global npm repository :

    cd src/301.tl && npm install && cd ../..

Bundle dependencies locally :

    cd src/301.tl && npm bundle && cd ../..


Configuration
-------------

301.tl uses "node-config" for its configuration.

    vi conf/$(hostname).js

Then add configuration options specific to your host with this format :

    exports.conf = {
      option: value,
    }

Available options :

* port (default 8001)
* host to listen (default '127.0.0.1')


Run
---

    node app.js
